1
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,940
=Ancient Bracelet=

2
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:44,380
=Episode 17=

3
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,660
=It's Alright; I'm Here=

4
00:00:50,430 --> 00:00:51,560
Hurry up, all of you.

5
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:53,070
Wu Luoluo?

6
00:00:54,030 --> 00:00:55,640
Weren't you locked away in the dungeon?

7
00:00:55,710 --> 00:00:56,790
How did you get out?

8
00:00:57,240 --> 00:00:59,070
You even slipped me Boneless Powder.

9
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:01,430
You can still recognize me?

10
00:01:01,470 --> 00:01:03,000
So, you're not entirely clueless.

11
00:01:03,430 --> 00:01:04,840
As for how I got out,

12
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:06,480
that's none of your concern.

13
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:07,710
We are both women here.

14
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:10,280
Why use such underhanded means?

15
00:01:12,310 --> 00:01:13,560
Underhanded?

16
00:01:15,710 --> 00:01:17,790
Why not speak of your fickle ways?

17
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:20,070
As Che's wife,

18
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:22,840
you slept with the ruler.

19
00:01:23,150 --> 00:01:25,310
I thought once you stayed
with the ruler,

20
00:01:25,430 --> 00:01:27,310
Che would cast you aside,

21
00:01:27,590 --> 00:01:29,350
so I used a little drug to help you.

22
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:31,000
Who would've thought

23
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:33,430
Che would care even more about you?

24
00:01:37,230 --> 00:01:39,000
How could you drug me?

25
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:41,070
If I desired you,

26
00:01:41,350 --> 00:01:42,870
I'd never stoop to such means.

27
00:01:44,430 --> 00:01:46,310
So, it was you who drugged me.

28
00:01:46,590 --> 00:01:49,280
You made me lose face before him.

29
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:52,950
I can make you suffer even more.

30
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:54,480
Once you're utterly disgraced,

31
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,853
the ruler will surely execute you,

32
00:01:55,864 --> 00:01:57,200
the woman he deems impure.

33
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,430
By then,

34
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,590
when you're gone,

35
00:01:59,950 --> 00:02:02,000
I'll be the one standing by Che's side.

36
00:02:02,070 --> 00:02:03,230
One day,

37
00:02:03,310 --> 00:02:05,400
he'll marry me.

38
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:10,400
My beauty,

39
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:11,840
don't you worry.

40
00:02:12,310 --> 00:02:13,960
I'll be gentle with you.

41
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:16,190
Stay back!

42
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,400
Get away!

43
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,310
Let go of me!

44
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,080
Move aside!

45
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:34,630
Step away!

46
00:02:34,630 --> 00:02:35,960
Don't touch me!

47
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,350
Zhaoli!

48
00:02:37,470 --> 00:02:38,310
It's me.

49
00:02:38,470 --> 00:02:39,310
I'm Ying Du.

50
00:02:40,310 --> 00:02:41,150
Ying Du...

51
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,680
It's all right now.

52
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,280
I'm here.

53
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:00,710
Let's go.

54
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:02,430
Hurry!

55
00:03:11,430 --> 00:03:12,270
Zhaoli.

56
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:13,740
Zhaoli.

57
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:16,710
Zhaoli.

58
00:03:19,030 --> 00:03:20,310
You're safe now, Zhaoli.

59
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:23,590
It's over.

60
00:03:24,190 --> 00:03:25,150
Let's go home.

61
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:41,120
It seems Ying Du
is not as powerful as before.

62
00:03:41,870 --> 00:03:43,430
My chance has finally come.

63
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:45,700
Your Highness,

64
00:03:45,750 --> 00:03:47,030
what should we do now?

65
00:03:47,150 --> 00:03:48,240
If the ruler finds out,

66
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,800
he will never let me off.

67
00:03:51,150 --> 00:03:52,520
Your Highness, I acted strictly

68
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,800
according to your instructions.

69
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:55,360
You will help me, won't you?

70
00:03:55,430 --> 00:03:56,280
Rest assured.

71
00:03:56,910 --> 00:03:58,150
With me here,

72
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:00,150
no harm will come to you.

73
00:04:01,390 --> 00:04:02,400
Thank you, Your Highness.

74
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,430
Because I'll never

75
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:12,910
let the ruler catch you.

76
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:47,430
You can't even guard yourself,

77
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,600
yet you claim you can kill me.

78
00:04:53,190 --> 00:04:54,360
That's a separate matter.

79
00:04:54,970 --> 00:04:56,240
Thank you for saving me today.

80
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,400
Don't move.

81
00:05:02,190 --> 00:05:03,100
Zhaoli,

82
00:05:03,100 --> 00:05:04,160
you don't need to thank me.

83
00:05:04,390 --> 00:05:05,360
No matter what happens,

84
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,510
I'll always keep you safe.

85
00:05:08,270 --> 00:05:10,000
But you don't know a single move.

86
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,160
If one day I'm gone,

87
00:05:11,310 --> 00:05:12,560
how will you protect yourself?

88
00:05:14,190 --> 00:05:15,030
(Ying Du,)

89
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:17,750
(you slaughtered my people,)

90
00:05:18,430 --> 00:05:19,430
(yet you shielded me)

91
00:05:20,830 --> 00:05:22,190
(and saved me)

92
00:05:22,950 --> 00:05:24,190
(from peril.)

93
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:27,830
(Which one of you is the real you?)

94
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,360
(Can I still trust you?)

95
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,440
(Zhaoli,)

96
00:05:34,892 --> 00:05:35,986
(before the truth is known,)

97
00:05:36,056 --> 00:05:37,165
(you can't trust him again.)

98
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,190
If you stop pestering me,

99
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:41,000
that will be the greatest protection.

100
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,190
But I can't help myself.

101
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:43,830
My heart belongs to you.

102
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,200
You rogue.

103
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,480
What are you doing?

104
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:56,070
The Bracelet is useless
to you right now.

105
00:05:56,369 --> 00:05:57,413
I'll take it back for now.

106
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,630
When the time is right,

107
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,070
I'll return it to you.

108
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,200
Ying Du,

109
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:09,000
you clearly know everything,

110
00:06:09,270 --> 00:06:10,510
yet you keep everything hidden.

111
00:06:11,750 --> 00:06:12,630
And this.

112
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,560
You can't heal it yourself.

113
00:06:14,571 --> 00:06:16,816
Does it have something to do
with the Bracelet's damage?

114
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,800
Are you concerned about me?

115
00:06:21,390 --> 00:06:23,800
I'm asking why the Bracelet broke.

116
00:06:25,070 --> 00:06:26,870
You keep saying I'm in danger;

117
00:06:26,870 --> 00:06:28,240
you told me to stay away from Che.

118
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:30,040
Is it because he might harm me,

119
00:06:30,270 --> 00:06:32,120
or are you trying to turn me
against him?

120
00:06:32,510 --> 00:06:34,360
So, you'd rather doubt me

121
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:37,270
than believe I'm sincere toward you?

122
00:06:38,510 --> 00:06:40,310
I just haven't seen it with my eyes.

123
00:06:42,310 --> 00:06:43,480
I trust no one.

124
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:46,720
I'll make you believe me.

125
00:06:48,430 --> 00:06:49,680
You should rest for now.

126
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,080
Your Majesty,

127
00:07:52,590 --> 00:07:53,460
we've found the two

128
00:07:53,470 --> 00:07:54,950
who insulted Zhaoli.

129
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:57,040
They are Lai and Hu
from the Wuyue tribe.

130
00:08:04,430 --> 00:08:05,480
You summoned me.

131
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:06,560
What's the matter?

132
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:09,520
Come here.

133
00:08:14,430 --> 00:08:15,270
Hu.

134
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:16,560
Lai.

135
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,680
What do you want to do to my people?

136
00:08:23,190 --> 00:08:24,600
Ying Du, let me go.

137
00:08:25,070 --> 00:08:27,000
Today, I'll teach you
a few self-defense moves.

138
00:08:27,950 --> 00:08:29,270
For times when I'm not around,

139
00:08:30,075 --> 00:08:31,469
they'll be enough to keep you safe.

140
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,040
Lai!

141
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:35,920
Lai!

142
00:08:37,220 --> 00:08:38,060
Lai!

143
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:41,510
What are you doing?

144
00:08:41,510 --> 00:08:42,630
You're out of your mind.

145
00:08:42,630 --> 00:08:43,870
How could you use my hands

146
00:08:43,870 --> 00:08:45,270
to harm my own people?

147
00:08:46,030 --> 00:08:46,910
Try it.

148
00:08:47,910 --> 00:08:48,840
Zhaoli.

149
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,150
Please, spare me.

150
00:08:50,150 --> 00:08:52,240
Zhaoli, spare me.

151
00:08:54,390 --> 00:08:55,390
Zhaoli.

152
00:08:55,390 --> 00:08:57,120
Zhaoli, spare me.

153
00:08:57,270 --> 00:08:58,360
No.

154
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,390
No, please.

155
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:01,120
Zhaoli.

156
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,790
Please, spare me.

157
00:09:03,750 --> 00:09:04,790
Zhaoli.

158
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:05,750
They hurt you.

159
00:09:05,750 --> 00:09:06,416
No.

160
00:09:06,427 --> 00:09:07,539
Don't let your heart soften.

161
00:09:07,550 --> 00:09:08,320
Zhaoli.

162
00:09:08,390 --> 00:09:09,320
Please, don't kill me.

163
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,160
Zhaoli.

164
00:09:10,170 --> 00:09:11,100
Please, don't kill me.

165
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,440
Please, don't kill me.

166
00:09:12,630 --> 00:09:13,820
Please, don't kill me.

167
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,080
Zhaoli.

168
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,750
Zhaoli, please don't kill me.

169
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,200
- Zhaoli.
- Grandmother.

170
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,750
It's me, your grandmother.

171
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:33,000
Grandmother.

172
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:42,240
Ying Du killed Grandmother.

173
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:44,550
He killed Grandmother.

174
00:09:48,670 --> 00:09:50,270
You killed Grandmother.

175
00:09:52,750 --> 00:09:57,400
♪Snow falls upon my brows,
blurring suddenly♪

176
00:09:59,230 --> 00:10:04,200
♪Memories turn,
forgiving time after time♪

177
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:08,940
♪Tears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter♪

178
00:10:08,940 --> 00:10:11,840
♪Hard to tell them apart♪

179
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:17,650
♪Vowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness♪

180
00:10:17,650 --> 00:10:21,350
♪In this life, I still run toward you♪

181
00:10:21,700 --> 00:10:24,050
♪No matter the homeward journey♪

182
00:10:24,050 --> 00:10:28,090
♪Falling to the deepest place
in your heart♪

183
00:10:28,090 --> 00:10:30,470
♪And that is enough♪

184
00:10:30,470 --> 00:10:34,260
♪Ahead lies a path without snow or wind♪

185
00:10:34,470 --> 00:10:37,230
♪Begonia blooms across the branches♪

186
